$ Representational state transfer
@ REST


REST tries to fix the problems with → development/web/service/SOAP.

REST uses → development/web/HTTP verbs (`GET`, `POST`, `PUT`, `DELETE` and `PATCH`) to create, change or delete content (aka CRUD operations).

